Package: matugen
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         libx11-6
Description: Material You color generation tool
 matugen is a Material You color palette generator that generates color
 schemes from images and applies them to various applications and desktop
 environments.
 .
 Features include:
  - Generate color palettes from images
  - Material Design 3 color system support
  - Multiple export formats (JSON, CSS, SCSS, etc.)
  - Integration with system theming tools
  - Perfect for auto-theming based on wallpaper colors
